"Skipped 1 entry stored in credsStore / credHelpers (the password lives in the OS keychain, not in the file)." = "已略過 1 個保存在 credsStore / credHelpers 中的項目（密碼保存在系統鑰匙圈中，不在檔案裡）。";
"Skipped %d entries stored in credsStore / credHelpers (passwords live in the OS keychain, not in the file)." = "已略過 %d 個保存在 credsStore / credHelpers 中的項目（密碼保存在系統鑰匙圈中，不在檔案裡）。";
